currency.blockTitle: The pool will pay all profit (including all uncle blocks).
currency.blocksTtileTwo: should confirm 120 blocks, you have to wait about 30 minutes
currency.faqOne: How to see how many times I pay and how much I have paid?
currency.faqOneAn: You can query historical payment data on the block chain browser.
currency.faqTwo: Why does the hashrate show instability? Isn't it correct?
currency.faqTwoAn: Because hashrate shown in the pool is calculated according to the shared value submitted by the machine, hashrate of the pool has fluctuation of about 10%-25% of the upper and lower parts. You can rest assured on it. You can contact us at any time if you have any questions.
currency.faqThree: When does the payment start? When will the profit be issued?
currency.faqThreeAn: The payment starts at 12:00 every day. Generally, it will be paid before 18:00(Pay the earnings of the previous day).
currency.faqFour: Why do my three miners only show one?
currency.faqFourAn: You can see if the name of the machine is the same, and the miner's name can not be one.
currency.faqFive: What is the rate of the pool?
currency.faqFiveAn: ETC and ETF's pool rate is 1%,HSR and LCH are free at present.
currency.faqSixAn: You can set it at random, usually within 15 characters or letters.
currency.faqSeven: What is the Paid in the 91Pool miner page?
currency.faqSevenAn: It is the amount of money dug yesterday
currency.faqEightAn: The immature profit is the contribution of your contribution share to the percentage of the allocated block, waiting for the full net confirmation number to be transferred to the unpaid proceeds.
currency.faqNine: How to change the double node？
currency.faqNineAn: Download the group file epools, then add it and change the wallet address to your own.
currency.faqTen: What else do I have to do with other questions?
currency.faqTenAn: You can contact our customer service staff through our QQ group. They will answer your questions.
